They ensure a consistent and efficient experience for you while visiting our Website or using our Services.{$LINE_BREAK} Cookies may be set by the Website (first-party cookies), or by third parties, such as those who serve content or provide advertising or analytics services on the website (third party cookies). These third parties can recognize you when you visit our website and also when you visit certain other websites.{$CLOSE_PARAGRAPH}{$START_HEADING_LEVEL5}What type of cookies do we use?{$CLOSE_HEADING_LEVEL5}{$START_HEADING_LEVEL6}Necessary cookies{$CLOSE_HEADING_LEVEL6}{$START_PARAGRAPH}Necessary cookies allow us to offer you the best possible experience when accessing and navigating through our Website and using its features.
